name: Figma Dashboard Templates UI kit - S8 Design System
description:
S8 Dashboard UI kit for Figma is a design library for mobile and desktop apps made of the same components and instances reused. Adjustable, Organized, Responsive design kit based on modular web application ideas. Scales from mobile to desktop. It comes with a wide range of dashboard ideas inside, which help to get better at designing natural responsive apps!


Website · Templates · Preview in Figma
